{"translation-revision-date":"2026-01-24 23:24:58+0000","generator":"GlotPress\/4.0.3","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=n > 1;","lang":"tr"},"API Key":["API Anahtar\u0131"],"Change Key":["Anahtar\u0131 De\u011fi\u015ftir"],"Use the %1$s button to verify that the key is accessible for search engines. Clicking on it should open the key file in your browser and show the API key.":["Anahtar\u0131n arama motorlar\u0131 i\u00e7in eri\u015filebilir oldu\u011funu do\u011frulamak i\u00e7in %1$s d\u00fc\u011fmesini kullan\u0131n. \u00dczerine t\u0131klad\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131zda anahtar dosyas\u0131 taray\u0131c\u0131n\u0131zda a\u00e7\u0131lmal\u0131 ve API anahtar\u0131 g\u00f6sterilmelidir."],"Check Key":["Anahtar\u0131 Kontrol Et"],"API Key Location":["API Anahtar\u0131 Konumu"],"The IndexNow API key proves the ownership of the site. It is generated automatically. You can change the key if it becomes known to third parties.":["IndexNow API anahtar\u0131 sitenin sahipli\u011fini kan\u0131tlar. Otomatik olarak olu\u015fturulur. Anahtar\u0131n \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcnc\u00fc \u015fah\u0131slar taraf\u0131ndan \u00f6\u011frenilmesi durumunda de\u011fi\u015ftirebilirsiniz."],"Too Many Requests":["\u00c7ok Fazla \u0130stek"],"URL slug placeholder\u0004hello-world":["merhaba-dunya"],"History":["Ge\u00e7mi\u015f"],"Forbidden":["Yasak"],"Accepted":["Kabul Edildi"],"Response":["Yan\u0131t"],"Manual":["Manuel"],"Clear History":["Ge\u00e7mi\u015fi Temizle"],"Submit posts from these post types automatically to the IndexNow API when a post is published, updated, or trashed.":["Bir g\u00f6nderi yay\u0131nland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda, g\u00fcncellendi\u011finde veya \u00e7\u00f6pe at\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda bu g\u00f6nderi t\u00fcrlerindeki g\u00f6nderileri otomatik olarak IndexNow API'sine g\u00f6nderin."],"Auto-Submit Post Types":["Yaz\u0131 T\u00fcrlerini Otomatik G\u00f6nder"],"Too Many Requests (potential Spam).":["\u00c7ok Fazla \u0130stek (potansiyel Spam)."],"The URLs don't belong to the host or the key is not matching the schema in the protocol.":["URL'ler ana makineye ait de\u011fil veya anahtar, protokoldeki \u015femayla e\u015fle\u015fmiyor."],"Unprocessable Entity":["Varl\u0131k i\u015flenemedi"],"The key was invalid (e.g. key not found, file found but key not in the file).":["Anahtar ge\u00e7ersiz (\u00f6r. anahtar bulunamad\u0131, dosya bulundu ancak anahtar dosyada yok)."],"The request was invalid.":["\u0130stek ge\u00e7ersizdi."],"Bad Request":["Ge\u00e7ersiz \u0130stek"],"The URL was successfully submitted to the IndexNow API, but the API key will be checked later.":["URL, IndexNow API'sine ba\u015far\u0131yla g\u00f6nderildi ancak API anahtar\u0131 daha sonra kontrol edilecek."],"The URL was successfully submitted to the IndexNow API.":["URL, IndexNow API'sine ba\u015far\u0131yla g\u00f6nderildi."],"Reasons":["Sebepler"],"Response Message":["Yan\u0131t Mesaj\u0131"],"Response Code Help":["Yan\u0131t Kodu Yard\u0131m\u0131"],"Auto":["Otomatik"],"Insert URLs to send to the IndexNow API (one per line, up to 10,000):":["IndexNow API'sine g\u00f6nderilecek URL'leri ekleyin (sat\u0131r ba\u015f\u0131na bir tane, en fazla 10.000):"],"No submissions yet.":["Hen\u00fcz ba\u015fvuru yok."],"Error: could not clear history.":["Hata: ge\u00e7mi\u015f temizlenemedi."],"An error occurred while submitting the URL.":["URL g\u00f6nderilirken bir hata olu\u015ftu."],"The last 100 IndexNow API requests.":["Son 100 IndexNow API iste\u011fi."],"Send URLs directly to the IndexNow API.":["URL'leri do\u011frudan IndexNow API'sine g\u00f6nderin."],"Submit URLs":["URL'leri G\u00f6nder"],"Time":["Zaman"],"Settings":["Ayarlar"],"OK":["Tamam"],"All":["T\u00fcm\u00fc"],"URL":["Link"],"Response Code":["Cevap Kodu"]}},"comment":{"reference":"assets\/admin\/js\/instantIndexingSettings.js"}}